Class DynamicBigDecimal

java.lang.Object
  org.gephi.data.attributes.type.DynamicType<BigDecimal>
      org.gephi.data.attributes.type.DynamicBigDecimal

public final class DynamicBigDecimal
extends DynamicType<BigDecimal>

Represents BigDecimal type which can have got different values in different time intervals.

Author:
Cezary Bartosiak
